It's funny how sweet I.N. looks here, but honestly besides Chan he might be the scariest one when gets angry. 

The clip of him getting angry with Changbin for again calling him by Yongbok (sp?) aka confusing him with Felix. Bro.. nah... Nah ... even Changbin might have gotten a little scared. 😂

In general, the group as a whole has such insane dualities in looks, sounds, and behavior. All the members have a sense of duality & it's very easy to spot well for most. I think Seungmin is the hardest, but it's there too. I love that I have been able to learn that since becoming a Stay. A combo of my Pscyh degree & being a Stay.... A thing of beauty and wonder. 😊
